dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Latin text on verso with caption title: Terra Sancta; p. 51. From: Ptolemaeus, Claudius, Geographia, (Basileae: Per Henricum Petrum, 1545), map no.51. This atlas is a reprint of Münster's 1540 and 1542 editions. Map is the same, only the title differs slightly.
